Package: STvEA
Type: Package
Title: Spatially-resolved Transcriptomics via Epitope Anchoring
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Kiya W.", "Govek", email = "govekk@pennmedicine.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: STvEA is an analysis pipeline for cleaning, clustering, and plotting CODEX and CITE-seq
  protein data, mapping a CODEX dataset to a matching CITE-seq dataset, and assessing colocalization
  of features using the Adjacency Score.
